1
00:00:10,960 --> 00:00:13,420
♪The maple mark on your skin♪

2
00:00:14,230 --> 00:00:17,040
♪The only proof we exist♪

3
00:00:18,210 --> 00:00:21,450
♪I stole you back from destiny♪

4
00:00:21,560 --> 00:00:24,430
♪But can I redeem myself♪

5
00:00:24,430 --> 00:00:26,540
♪I don't care what fate foretells♪

6
00:00:26,750 --> 00:00:30,330
♪Or how rough the road may be♪

7
00:00:30,340 --> 00:00:33,280
♪Stay, I'll fight for you♪

8
00:00:33,610 --> 00:00:37,660
♪That's all I'll ever do♪

9
00:00:37,760 --> 00:00:39,890
♪If life is just a show♪

10
00:00:39,890 --> 00:00:42,650
♪I'll stay with you till the end♪

11
00:00:42,650 --> 00:00:44,980
♪I'm scared we'll wake up alone♪

12
00:00:44,980 --> 00:00:47,960
♪So don't let this dream end♪

13
00:00:47,960 --> 00:00:52,420
♪In my bones, in my heart♪

14
00:00:52,420 --> 00:00:54,100
♪I know I'll have to leave♪

15
00:00:54,100 --> 00:00:55,670
♪You must not leave my side♪

16
00:00:55,670 --> 00:00:57,260
♪No place can hold us in♪

17
00:00:57,260 --> 00:01:01,910
♪Not when it's you and me♪

18
00:01:06,890 --> 00:01:10,400
♪Forever♪

19
00:01:11,490 --> 00:01:15,250
♪In my soul♪

20
00:01:17,260 --> 00:01:23,300
=This Palace Maid Isn't Very Calm=
=Episode 9=

21
00:01:26,310 --> 00:01:28,640
Hui, your outfit today…

22
00:01:29,040 --> 00:01:31,000
Even the maids

23
00:01:31,000 --> 00:01:32,640
outshine you.

24
00:01:36,590 --> 00:01:37,950
Forgive me.

25
00:01:38,710 --> 00:01:40,680
I'm still recovering.

26
00:01:41,070 --> 00:01:42,920
No energy to dress up.

27
00:01:44,120 --> 00:01:45,350
But Liu,

28
00:01:45,680 --> 00:01:48,280
you look splendid today.

29
00:01:48,840 --> 00:01:50,510
A gift from Consort Duan.

30
00:01:50,510 --> 00:01:51,560
Of course it's fine.

31
00:01:51,920 --> 00:01:53,120
She summoned me

32
00:01:53,120 --> 00:01:55,350
after I entered the palace.

33
00:01:55,870 --> 00:01:57,150
This is just one

34
00:01:57,150 --> 00:01:59,230
of the many gifts she gave me.

35
00:02:00,230 --> 00:02:02,870
I'll show you later.

36
00:02:04,230 --> 00:02:06,480
Consort Lan has arrived.

37
00:02:19,430 --> 00:02:21,520
Greetings,

38
00:02:22,080 --> 00:02:23,590
I hosted this banquet

39
00:02:24,000 --> 00:02:27,080
to see your grace and talent.

40
00:02:28,150 --> 00:02:29,120
Little did I expect

41
00:02:29,560 --> 00:02:32,280
your petty bickering.

42
00:02:33,520 --> 00:02:34,470
Rise.

43
00:02:34,470 --> 00:02:36,470
Thank you, Your Highness.

44
00:02:39,030 --> 00:02:39,870
Are you

45
00:02:40,430 --> 00:02:41,430
Liu Mei?

46
00:02:42,840 --> 00:02:44,910
Who chose that outfit?

47
00:02:45,430 --> 00:02:46,360
Your Highness.

48
00:02:46,520 --> 00:02:48,710
Consort Duan gifted it.

49
00:02:49,240 --> 00:02:50,840
I dressed formally

50
00:02:50,840 --> 00:02:52,870
for today's banquet.

51
00:02:54,590 --> 00:02:56,120
Unbelievable.

52
00:02:56,360 --> 00:02:58,470
You're not yet titled,

53
00:02:58,960 --> 00:03:01,910
yet you dare wear consort colors?

54
00:03:03,560 --> 00:03:04,400
I…

55
00:03:04,520 --> 00:03:06,400
I didn't know.

56
00:03:06,400 --> 00:03:07,590
Please forgive me.

57
00:03:08,400 --> 00:03:10,080
If you don't know the rules,

58
00:03:10,080 --> 00:03:12,150
you'd better learn them.

59
00:03:12,710 --> 00:03:13,550
Biqing.

60
00:03:15,560 --> 00:03:16,400
Yes.

61
00:03:18,710 --> 00:03:19,750
Please come with me.

62
00:03:20,150 --> 00:03:22,360
Let me show you some manners.

63
00:03:23,680 --> 00:03:24,520
Your Highness.

64
00:03:25,710 --> 00:03:26,550
Your Highness.

65
00:03:27,240 --> 00:03:28,680
Please, have mercy.

66
00:03:29,000 --> 00:03:29,870
Your Highness.

67
00:03:31,400 --> 00:03:32,590
The show's over.

68
00:03:33,560 --> 00:03:34,400
Sit down.

69
00:04:25,360 --> 00:04:26,390
My face.

70
00:04:26,630 --> 00:04:27,750
My face.

71
00:04:31,560 --> 00:04:32,630
What's going on?

72
00:04:33,310 --> 00:04:34,870
You're about to meet the Emperor.

73
00:04:34,870 --> 00:04:36,120
Are you prepared?

74
00:04:36,480 --> 00:04:38,070
Ma'am, my face.

75
00:04:38,070 --> 00:04:38,910
You…

76
00:04:39,120 --> 00:04:40,720
How did this happen?

77
00:04:42,630 --> 00:04:44,310
Get Physician Zhang, quickly.

78
00:04:45,040 --> 00:04:45,950
But I…

79
00:04:46,680 --> 00:04:47,520
But what?

80
00:04:47,870 --> 00:04:49,830
Do you want to go looking like that

81
00:04:50,000 --> 00:04:51,830
and be punished for offending him?

82
00:04:52,560 --> 00:04:54,000
Stay here and recover.

83
00:04:54,390 --> 00:04:56,510
Ma'am, I've prepared so long

84
00:04:56,510 --> 00:04:58,430
for this day.

85
00:04:58,600 --> 00:04:59,460
Please.

86
00:04:59,510 --> 00:05:00,830
I know.

87
00:05:02,000 --> 00:05:03,800
Miss Liu Mei had a fever last night,

88
00:05:04,190 --> 00:05:05,360
and now this.

89
00:05:05,360 --> 00:05:07,070
Why is everything going wrong

90
00:05:07,070 --> 00:05:08,480
right before the audience?

91
00:05:20,360 --> 00:05:22,430
A gift from the Empress Dowager.

92
00:05:24,070 --> 00:05:26,190
Thank you, Her Highness.

93
00:05:31,070 --> 00:05:32,310
Wait.

94
00:05:35,510 --> 00:05:36,350
Hui.

95
00:05:36,510 --> 00:05:38,240
The audience is about to begin.

96
00:05:38,430 --> 00:05:39,360
But you…

97
00:05:40,310 --> 00:05:41,600
I feel uneasy

98
00:05:41,600 --> 00:05:43,430
and couldn't sleep last night.

99
00:05:45,390 --> 00:05:46,240
What happened to Yunxi

100
00:05:46,240 --> 00:05:48,120
was her own doing.

101
00:05:48,160 --> 00:05:49,360
Liu Mei's arrogance

102
00:05:49,360 --> 00:05:50,600
offended Consort Lan.

103
00:05:50,600 --> 00:05:52,160
I may have played a part,

104
00:05:52,190 --> 00:05:54,830
but it was her own recklessness.

105
00:05:55,560 --> 00:05:56,630
But Xiao Rou...

106
00:05:57,800 --> 00:05:59,630
She was always gentle and prudent.

107
00:06:00,040 --> 00:06:01,240
She didn't deserve this.

108
00:06:01,240 --> 00:06:04,070
Xiao Rou is just allergic to garden balsam.

109
00:06:04,230 --> 00:06:05,390
She'll be fine in a few days.

110
00:06:05,390 --> 00:06:06,230
Don't worry.

111
00:06:06,510 --> 00:06:07,390
Besides,

112
00:06:07,390 --> 00:06:08,600
it might be a blessing

113
00:06:08,600 --> 00:06:09,720
in disguise.

114
00:06:10,310 --> 00:06:11,750
What do you mean?

115
00:06:16,630 --> 00:06:20,000
I could've been much harsher

116
00:06:20,120 --> 00:06:21,430
to force her out early.

117
00:06:21,800 --> 00:06:22,640
Uh…

118
00:06:23,310 --> 00:06:24,830
Don't overthink.

119
00:06:24,830 --> 00:06:27,120
Are you wearing the sachet I gave you?

120
00:06:31,720 --> 00:06:33,870
Make sure you have it.

121
00:06:33,920 --> 00:06:35,360
It'll bring you luck.

122
00:06:38,240 --> 00:06:39,240
I should go.

123
00:06:45,390 --> 00:06:48,120
(In the novel,
Xiao Rou stunned the Emperor)

124
00:06:48,120 --> 00:06:49,480
(and was titled First Attendant.)

125
00:06:49,510 --> 00:06:52,410
(Yunxi used a sachet to attract butterflies
and catch the Emperor's eye,)

126
00:06:52,410 --> 00:06:53,920
(earning the same rank.)

127
00:06:54,040 --> 00:06:55,750
(Liu Mei, backed by Consort Duan,)

128
00:06:55,750 --> 00:06:57,360
(was initially titled Noble Lady.)

129
00:06:57,360 --> 00:06:59,830
(Only the heroine struggled
to earn favor.)

130
00:07:00,360 --> 00:07:03,120
(I've set everything up for you.)

131
00:07:03,120 --> 00:07:05,720
(Please don't fail me.)

132
00:07:10,390 --> 00:07:12,680
Zhi Hui greets Your Majesty,

133
00:07:12,750 --> 00:07:14,680
Your Highness.

134
00:07:32,600 --> 00:07:34,000
Why a bee?

135
00:07:36,070 --> 00:07:37,270
Your Majesty,

136
00:07:37,600 --> 00:07:41,190
I heard that in ancient times,

137
00:07:41,190 --> 00:07:43,600
beauties draw butterflies.

138
00:07:44,160 --> 00:07:47,070
But this lady here

139
00:07:47,120 --> 00:07:48,480
attracts bees.

140
00:07:48,480 --> 00:07:50,830
Butterflies are spiritual creatures.

141
00:07:51,360 --> 00:07:55,040
They wouldn't be drawn to mediocrity.

142
00:07:55,560 --> 00:07:57,750
That's true.

143
00:07:58,160 --> 00:07:59,000
However,

144
00:07:59,010 --> 00:08:00,600
I once read in ancient texts

145
00:08:00,600 --> 00:08:01,600
that bees

146
00:08:01,750 --> 00:08:03,480
are considered divine insects.

147
00:08:03,870 --> 00:08:05,190
They feed on dew and nectar,

148
00:08:05,190 --> 00:08:06,510
working with tireless loyalty.

149
00:08:07,160 --> 00:08:09,560
People see them as symbols of good luck,

150
00:08:09,560 --> 00:08:12,720
hard work, longevity, and wealth.

151
00:08:13,310 --> 00:08:15,510
Today, the flowers in full bloom.

152
00:08:15,830 --> 00:08:17,480
To attract a divine insect

153
00:08:17,560 --> 00:08:19,680
is truly my honor.

154
00:08:25,750 --> 00:08:27,310
She is beautiful,

155
00:08:27,310 --> 00:08:28,680
elegant, and wise.

156
00:08:28,680 --> 00:08:30,190
Reminds me

157
00:08:30,190 --> 00:08:32,600
of the late Emperor's Consort Xian.

158
00:08:33,550 --> 00:08:34,600
Your Majesty,

159
00:08:34,600 --> 00:08:35,720
what do you think?

160
00:08:36,120 --> 00:08:37,080
Mother is right.

161
00:08:38,600 --> 00:08:39,790
For the Dowager's favor,

162
00:08:40,030 --> 00:08:41,600
title her First Attendant.

163
00:08:42,600 --> 00:08:43,510
Her honorary title

164
00:08:44,030 --> 00:08:44,960
shall be "Hui."

165
00:08:45,600 --> 00:08:46,870
Thank you, Your Majesty.

166
00:08:46,960 --> 00:08:49,030
Thank you, Your Highness.

167
00:09:01,150 --> 00:09:02,670
First Attendant

168
00:09:03,030 --> 00:09:04,600
and a title too?

169
00:09:05,120 --> 00:09:06,270
Seriously?

170
00:09:07,030 --> 00:09:08,270
She's not worthy.

171
00:09:08,910 --> 00:09:10,150
Calm down, Your Highness.

172
00:09:10,480 --> 00:09:11,600
If I may say so,

173
00:09:11,790 --> 00:09:13,600
the promotions today

174
00:09:13,600 --> 00:09:14,720
were just for show.

175
00:09:15,270 --> 00:09:17,240
Her honorary title was

176
00:09:17,440 --> 00:09:20,000
to please the Empress Dowager.

177
00:09:20,440 --> 00:09:23,320
His Majesty barely noticed her.

178
00:09:23,720 --> 00:09:24,720
For some reason,

179
00:09:25,390 --> 00:09:27,270
the moment I see her face,

180
00:09:27,630 --> 00:09:29,200
I cannot stand her.

181
00:09:29,870 --> 00:09:31,360
Since the last banquet,

182
00:09:31,600 --> 00:09:33,000
most of the new candidates

183
00:09:33,080 --> 00:09:35,630
have already sided with you.

184
00:09:36,030 --> 00:09:38,360
Only Hui stays aloof,

185
00:09:38,440 --> 00:09:39,670
not even paying respects.

186
00:09:40,070 --> 00:09:41,550
Your Highness finds her displeasing,

187
00:09:41,870 --> 00:09:43,360
and I find her an eyesore too.

188
00:09:50,320 --> 00:09:54,360
Well, you don't look well.

189
00:09:55,910 --> 00:09:56,790
No wonder.

190
00:09:57,480 --> 00:09:59,480
With new arrivals,

191
00:09:59,960 --> 00:10:02,840
we old ones

192
00:10:03,320 --> 00:10:06,240
will be even lonelier.

193
00:10:07,510 --> 00:10:09,910
I control the harem.

194
00:10:10,320 --> 00:10:11,720
If I wish for company,

195
00:10:11,840 --> 00:10:13,390
I'll get it.

196
00:10:14,480 --> 00:10:16,440
But you…

197
00:10:16,910 --> 00:10:20,390
Heard you called a physician again?

198
00:10:21,270 --> 00:10:23,270
Is the pregnancy

199
00:10:23,910 --> 00:10:25,320
unstable again?

200
00:10:28,600 --> 00:10:31,120
New girls will soon

201
00:10:31,120 --> 00:10:33,360
serve His Majesty.

202
00:10:33,390 --> 00:10:35,480
So, take care

203
00:10:35,840 --> 00:10:38,000
and stop pulling that.

204
00:10:38,440 --> 00:10:40,790
After all,
His Majesty has new options now.

205
00:10:41,270 --> 00:10:43,960
Your tricks

206
00:10:46,510 --> 00:10:49,270
won't last forever.

207
00:11:10,750 --> 00:11:11,910
Greetings,

208
00:11:12,000 --> 00:11:12,960
Your Highnesses.

209
00:11:13,510 --> 00:11:14,480
Your Highness.

210
00:11:14,480 --> 00:11:17,200
Dinner is buckwheat rice

211
00:11:17,670 --> 00:11:18,550
and corn cakes.

212
00:11:19,120 --> 00:11:19,960
Mm.

213
00:11:20,240 --> 00:11:22,150
Looks light and appetizing.

214
00:11:22,480 --> 00:11:23,320
Mother,

215
00:11:23,480 --> 00:11:25,670
the Imperial Clinic came
for a follow-up yesterday.

216
00:11:25,670 --> 00:11:26,630
Did they say anything?

217
00:11:26,630 --> 00:11:27,470
Yes.

218
00:11:27,840 --> 00:11:30,480
They vindicated Ye Jin.

219
00:11:30,870 --> 00:11:32,030
After the follow-up,

220
00:11:32,030 --> 00:11:35,270
they confirmed
her therapeutic diet works.

221
00:11:35,780 --> 00:11:36,670
Also,

222
00:11:36,670 --> 00:11:38,870
your manual is scientifically sound.

223
00:11:39,120 --> 00:11:40,080
Not a work of hearsay.

224
00:11:40,270 --> 00:11:42,000
I've had it copied

225
00:11:42,320 --> 00:11:44,120
and distributed

226
00:11:44,120 --> 00:11:45,870
to help the people.

227
00:11:46,630 --> 00:11:48,030
You are truly benevolent.

228
00:11:49,030 --> 00:11:50,200
Son.

229
00:11:51,240 --> 00:11:52,080
Mother.

230
00:11:52,360 --> 00:11:54,270
I'm much recovered now.

231
00:11:54,630 --> 00:11:56,670
You don't need to stay by my side.

232
00:11:56,840 --> 00:11:58,480
Return to your residence.

233
00:11:59,030 --> 00:12:01,150
Your brother promised to make you

234
00:12:01,150 --> 00:12:02,550
an Imperial Prince once you marry.

235
00:12:02,960 --> 00:12:05,080
It is time you take a wife

236
00:12:05,480 --> 00:12:07,120
and continued our family line.

237
00:12:07,440 --> 00:12:08,290
(This is not right.)

238
00:12:08,360 --> 00:12:10,480
(This part came too early.)

239
00:12:10,750 --> 00:12:11,590
Mother.

240
00:12:11,960 --> 00:12:13,630
I do not wish to marry.

241
00:12:13,910 --> 00:12:15,510
Nonsense.

242
00:12:15,720 --> 00:12:17,360
Every man gets married.

243
00:12:17,760 --> 00:12:18,640
Right.

244
00:12:18,670 --> 00:12:20,630
Did you review the portraits?

245
00:12:20,870 --> 00:12:21,960
Anyone caught your eye?

246
00:12:21,960 --> 00:12:23,320
No interest.

247
00:12:23,750 --> 00:12:24,750
I haven't looked at all.

248
00:12:24,750 --> 00:12:25,600
Ridiculous.

249
00:12:28,080 --> 00:12:30,200
I'll choose with you.

250
00:12:31,000 --> 00:12:33,080
This must be settled today.

251
00:12:33,240 --> 00:12:34,320
Mother.

252
00:12:39,150 --> 00:12:40,440
(This is absurd.)

253
00:12:40,440 --> 00:12:42,270
(Choosing a wife from portraits.)

254
00:12:42,270 --> 00:12:43,240
(Won't be easy.)

255
00:12:43,240 --> 00:12:44,080
Look.

256
00:12:44,440 --> 00:12:45,480
This one has fine features.

257
00:12:45,840 --> 00:12:46,870
She is worthy of my son.

258
00:12:47,030 --> 00:12:48,240
Too cold.

259
00:12:48,320 --> 00:12:49,480
Like a block of ice.

260
00:12:49,910 --> 00:12:50,960
Not to my liking.

261
00:12:50,960 --> 00:12:52,150
What about this one?

262
00:12:52,510 --> 00:12:53,840
She has a warm smile.

263
00:12:54,120 --> 00:12:55,550
Seems cheerful.

264
00:12:56,320 --> 00:12:57,160
Mother.

265
00:12:57,240 --> 00:12:58,510
Look more closely.

266
00:12:58,630 --> 00:12:59,600
Her mouth's crooked.

267
00:13:05,080 --> 00:13:06,150
And this one?

268
00:13:06,510 --> 00:13:07,790
She looks virtuous and kind.

269
00:13:08,030 --> 00:13:09,720
Quite approachable.

270
00:13:10,510 --> 00:13:11,440
I think

271
00:13:11,750 --> 00:13:13,200
she looks more like

272
00:13:13,900 --> 00:13:15,290
a strict nanny.

273
00:13:20,600 --> 00:13:21,870
Son,

274
00:13:22,440 --> 00:13:23,630
I selected

275
00:13:23,790 --> 00:13:25,870
these girls from noble families

276
00:13:25,870 --> 00:13:26,930
for you,

277
00:13:27,510 --> 00:13:28,510
but somehow,

278
00:13:28,510 --> 00:13:29,480
you reject them all.

279
00:13:29,870 --> 00:13:31,960
Are you defying me?

280
00:13:33,390 --> 00:13:34,270
Mother.

281
00:13:34,750 --> 00:13:37,080
I'm not defying you.

282
00:13:37,270 --> 00:13:38,150
I...

283
00:13:38,550 --> 00:13:40,390
I just don't want to marry.

284
00:13:40,750 --> 00:13:41,720
Enough.

285
00:13:41,960 --> 00:13:43,790
At your age,

286
00:13:43,790 --> 00:13:45,360
your brother had a daughter already.

287
00:13:45,510 --> 00:13:48,320
The second batch of candidates
is already here.

288
00:13:48,320 --> 00:13:49,120
Mother.

289
00:13:49,240 --> 00:13:51,390
I am not

290
00:13:51,670 --> 00:13:53,670
my brother.

291
00:13:58,390 --> 00:13:59,550
If you will not choose,

292
00:13:59,870 --> 00:14:02,030
I will choose one for you.

293
00:14:02,480 --> 00:14:03,390
This girl's

294
00:14:03,960 --> 00:14:05,910
the eldest daughter
of the Great General.

295
00:14:06,080 --> 00:14:07,080
Tongjia Baozhu.

296
00:14:07,270 --> 00:14:09,320
She's beautiful

297
00:14:09,550 --> 00:14:10,870
and high-born.

298
00:14:10,960 --> 00:14:12,550
Perfect for you.

299
00:14:13,120 --> 00:14:13,960
But she...

300
00:14:14,030 --> 00:14:15,030
No but.

301
00:14:15,030 --> 00:14:16,030
It's settled.

302
00:14:16,200 --> 00:14:18,360
I'll summon her

303
00:14:18,510 --> 00:14:19,440
so you can meet.

304
00:14:24,750 --> 00:14:25,840
Isn't she great?

305
00:14:26,600 --> 00:14:27,440
Yes.

306
00:14:28,480 --> 00:14:30,270
I think so too.

307
00:14:36,230 --> 00:14:38,670
♪I am but an outsider♪

308
00:14:38,710 --> 00:14:40,870
♪Yet something drags me deeper♪

309
00:14:41,110 --> 00:14:45,150
♪Outwit the world but not the way we meet♪

310
00:14:45,150 --> 00:14:49,390
♪Splendid blooms line deadly ground♪

311
00:14:53,670 --> 00:14:56,910
♪Life's a phantom, yet I find you♪

312
00:14:57,070 --> 00:15:00,470
♪In a world of lies, you're all that's clear♪

313
00:15:00,470 --> 00:15:02,990
♪I know how this story ends♪

314
00:15:02,990 --> 00:15:07,550
♪I still want what's in your eyes♪

315
00:15:07,870 --> 00:15:11,990
♪Truth or lie—I can't tell♪

316
00:15:16,950 --> 00:15:20,270
♪You hide it all behind your lines♪

317
00:15:20,270 --> 00:15:23,550
♪So familiar, yet out of reach♪

318
00:15:23,750 --> 00:15:26,830
♪A history that no one can search♪

319
00:15:27,070 --> 00:15:30,350
♪Like you drift in from another star♪

320
00:15:30,390 --> 00:15:32,150
♪I am but an outsider♪

321
00:15:32,150 --> 00:15:34,390
♪Yet something drags me deeper♪

322
00:15:34,390 --> 00:15:38,430
♪Outwit the world but not the way we meet♪

323
00:15:38,430 --> 00:15:43,110
♪Splendid blooms line deadly ground♪

324
00:15:47,030 --> 00:15:50,430
♪Life's a phantom, yet I find you♪

325
00:15:50,430 --> 00:15:53,790
♪In a world of lies, you're all that's clear♪

326
00:15:53,790 --> 00:15:56,270
♪I know how this story ends♪

327
00:15:56,270 --> 00:16:00,430
♪I still want what's in your eyes♪

328
00:16:00,430 --> 00:16:03,710
♪When it's over and I'm gone♪

329
00:16:03,710 --> 00:16:07,510
♪Please forget me and move on♪

330
00:16:07,510 --> 00:16:13,750
♪Just let this absurd dream fade♪

331
00:16:16,910 --> 00:16:25,270
♪Snow hides our tracks♪

332
00:16:28,830 --> 00:16:38,550
♪When do I finally wake♪
